{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"접근성","mdn_url":"/ko/docs/Glossary/Accessibility","locale":"ko","native":"한국어","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>웹 접근성</strong>(Accessibility, <strong>A11Y</strong>)은 신체적, 기술적 제약사항에도 불구하고 충분히 사용 가능한 웹사이트를 만드는 것을 말합니다. 웹 접근성은 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/W3C\">W3C <small>(en-US)</small></a>의 <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Glossary/WAI\">Web Accessibility Initiative <small>(en-US)</small></a>(WAI)가 공식적으로 정의하고 논의합니다.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"더_알아보기","title":"더 알아보기","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"일반_지식","title":"일반 지식","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/Accessibility\">MDN의 접근성 자료</a></li>\n <li>위키백과 <a title=\"웹 접근성\" href=\"https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/웹_접근성\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">웹 접근성</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"웹_접근성_학습","title":"웹 접근성 학습","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Learn/Accessibility\">MDN에서 접근성 학습하기</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://webaim.org/\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">Web Accessibility In Mind</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"기술_참고서","title":"기술 참고서","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ko/docs/Web/Accessibility/ARIA\">MDN ARIA 문서</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/WAI/\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">Web Accessibility Initiative 홈페이지</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria/\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">WAI-ARIA 권고안</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"더 알아보기","id":"더_알아보기"}],"summary":"웹 접근성(Accessibility, A11Y)은 신체적, 기술적 제약사항에도 불구하고 충분히 사용 가능한 웹사이트를 만드는 것을 말합니다. 웹 접근성은 W3C (en-US)의 Web Accessibility Initiative (en-US)(WAI)가 공식적으로 정의하고 논의합니다.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Accessibility","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"Accessibility","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Accesibilidad","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"Accessibilité","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Accessibility (アクセシビリティ)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Accessibility","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Acessibilidade","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"Доступность","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"Accessibility","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"},{"title":"Accessibility","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)"}],"source":{"folder":"ko/glossary/accessibility","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ko/glossary/accessibility/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ko/docs/Glossary","title":"용어 사전"},{"uri":"/ko/docs/Glossary/Accessibility","title":"접근성"}],"pageTitle":"접근성 - 용어 사전 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}